query:
SELECT 
  pwi.id,
  pwi.waveId,
  pwi.productId,
  pwi.totalQuantity,
  pwi.pickedQuantity,
  pwi.status,
  p.sku,
  p.description
FROM pickingWaveItems pwi
INNER JOIN products p ON pwi.productId = p.id
WHERE pwi.waveId = (SELECT id FROM pickingWaves WHERE waveNumber = 'OS-20260121-0001')
ORDER BY pwi.id;
